LAMMPS (3 Mar 2020)
# Alpha
clear
units		real
dimension 3
boundary        p p p
atom_style	charge
newton on
read_data       O_31.lmp
  triclinic box = (0 0 0) to (13.552 11.7355 22.15) with tilt (-6.7755 0 0)
